Package: esmpowersim
Title: Power and Design Simulation for Event- and Location-Contingent Experience Sampling
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Yury", "Shevchenko", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3397-8465"))
Description: Reproducible simulator and design-planning tool for intensive
    longitudinal (ESM/EMA) studies in which the number of observations per
    person is a random variable driven by an event- or geofence-triggered
    sampling process. Implements the preregistered data-generating mechanism,
    fits the multilevel AR(1) model class, and reports power, precision,
    Type-S/Type-M error, convergence, and the distribution of effective
    observations per person. Companion to the methods paper.
